keyFacts: The email chain contains a confidentiality notice stating it is the property of Jeffrey Epstein.
The notice indicates the communication may be attorney-client privileged and constitutes inside information.
The emails discuss travel between Miami, New York, and West Palm Beach in January 2010.
The correspondence mentions casting appointments, a Maxim magazine party, and editorial work.
